text: Woo caagidiy baxxaqqa koh hayneeh kol maaqne tonnaay dulmih caddok edde tatreeniih biyaaken num dulmik kaal baaheenih innah tanim keenil baahaamih idini kaah yontocowwimeeh wohul dambi kaa mayabbixa, tohuk lakal woo mari kaat qagteeh dulmih caddok kaat tatrek diggah yalli kaa cate leeh kaa qokle-le, diggah Yalli dambi leelah qafu abeey dambi cabtili kinni
